    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/e7e3f79ca7c84c011597b428937f8453.avif?t=1772251805\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras_big/e7e3f79ca7c84c011597b428937f8453.webp?t=1772251805 width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pixel dungeon是一款快节奏，集多人社交与VR冒险于一体的动作大作。在这里，地牢探索、真实的物理战斗与好友间的狂欢完美融合。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆 <strong>Meta Quest官方推荐</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以4.8分超高口碑，Pixel Dungeon荣膺 <strong>Meta 2025 年度最佳动作、冒险游戏</strong>。加入我们的社区，亲身体验这款 Meta Quest 必玩的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ <strong>组队开黑，地牢狂欢</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持4人组队探险，或在10人大厅与全员一起狂欢！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跨版本联机</strong>:完整版玩家可以邀请尚未购买的朋友，一同探索<strong>整个地牢</strong>！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/ff91504331bff4050afc976ca9f977a9.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/ff91504331bff4050afc976ca9f977a9.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/ff91504331bff4050afc976ca9f977a9.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥史诗级Boss战</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四大Boss等你挑战：</strong>骷髅王狂挥巨斧，感受撞击。幽魂领主发射子弹，紧追不舍。战斗一触即发！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>二阶段</strong>：坠天使化身巨眼怪物狂扫死亡镭射；时间之神震碎地面，所有人跌入崭新竞技场——战斗升级炸翻天！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/28cd4f75f5952070737fd179706d0e39.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/28cd4f75f5952070737fd179706d0e39.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/28cd4f75f5952070737fd179706d0e39.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️终极武器库 &amp; 英雄传奇</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挥舞</strong>武士刀、利爪和弓箭，每次攻击都真实异常！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss武器：</strong>挥舞传说级Boss武器<strong>，</strong>粉碎敌人，主宰战场！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/629bae5b501a6551dc36819b57162c92.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/629bae5b501a6551dc36819b57162c92.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/629bae5b501a6551dc36819b57162c92.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特英雄</strong>：猎魔人、黑骑士、鸟人？选择专属英雄，开启传奇之路！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/8cdcd1fbaffa038436dcd46777a9f4a4.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/8cdcd1fbaffa038436dcd46777a9f4a4.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/8cdcd1fbaffa038436dcd46777a9f4a4.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
